  <abstract>
    <p>
      This book introduces quantitative research in the scientific and health
      disciplines, with an emphasis on introductory statistics.
      The research process is broken into six steps which provide the framework
      for the content. The book targets first-year undergraduate students in
      science, health, and engineering. Statistical output is from jamovi
      (free to download and use).
    </p>
